OL,3,CTwo former hospital staff challenge
OL,4,Cconvictions for mistreating patients
OL,6,FTwo staff members convicted of
OL,7,Fmistreating patients at a County
OL,8,FDurham specialist hospital have
OL,9,Fchallenged their convictions at the
OL,10,FCourt of Appeal.
OL,12,FPeter Bennett, 55, and Matthew Banner,
OL,13,F44, were found guilty of ill-treatment
OL,14,Fof patients at Whorlton Hall - an
OL,15,Findependent unit for people with
OL,16,Fcomplex needs near Barnard Castle - in
OL,17,FJanuary 2024.
