OL,3,CTwo former hospital staff challenge
OL,4,Cconvictions for mistreating patients
OL,6,FWhorlton Hall was the subject of a BBC
OL,7,FPanorama investigation which aimed to
OL,8,Fexpose poor treatment of patients at
OL,9,Fthe hospital in 2019.
OL,11,FThe facility has since closed.
OL,13,FDuring a hearing on Friday, lawyers
OL,14,Frepresenting Bennett and Banner
OL,15,Fchallenged the convictions arguing
OL,16,Fthat their actions "did not meet the
OL,17,Ftest for ill-treatment".
