OL,3,CTwo former hospital staff challenge
OL,4,Cconvictions for mistreating patients
OL,6,FLord Justice Singh, sitting alongside
OL,7,FMrs Justice May and Mr Justice
OL,8,FGriffiths, said judges would give
OL,9,Ftheir ruling over the appeals at a
OL,10,Flater date.
OL,12,FAt a sentencing hearing in January
OL,13,F2024, Bennett was sentenced to a four-
OL,14,Fmonth jail term suspended for 18
OL,15,Fmonths, on two charges of ill-
OL,16,Ftreatment.
OL,18,FBanner was also sentenced to a four-
OL,19,Fmonth jail term suspended for 18
OL,20,Fmonths relating to five charges of ill-
OL,21,Ftreatment.
